MERN - pre-dev & npm installations
Establish project and backend

$
mkdir my-app
cd my-app

$/my-app
npm init
npm install express
npm install nodemon
npm install morgan
npm install -g mongoose@5.13.0
npm install bcrypt
npm install jsonwebtoken
npm install dotenv
npm install express-jwt
npm install uuid

Client

$/my-app
mkdir client
cd client

$/my-app/client
npx create-react-app .
npm install react-router-dom@6.2.2
npm install axios

cd ..
code .


From Code Editor

Add files:

.env
.gitignore
.server.js
>routes
>models

>client
	>components


.package.json
add "proxy": "http://0.0.0.0:9000"
